content: A new proposal has been announced: lint internal hashmap iteration #465. It will be announced at the next meeting to try and draw attention to it, but usually MCPs are not discussed during triage meetings. If you think this would benefit from discussion amongst the team, consider proposing a design meeting.

yes :sweat_smile:
